ALSA: Au88x0 - Fix channels swapping of 4 channels playback

Fix channels swapping of 4 channels playback by
using vortex_adbdma_stopfifo instead of vortex_adbdma_pausefifo
for SNDRV_PCM_TRIGGER_STOP event

